---
import GopediaWorldTree from '../projects/GopediaWorldTree.astro';
---

<header class="relative z-[2] pt-16 pb-16 md:pt-20 md:pb-24 lg:pt-[80px] lg:pb-[160px] overflow-hidden bg-[var(--paper)]">
  <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr_1fr] gap-10 lg:gap-[60px] items-center">

      <!-- Text column -->
      <div class="min-w-0">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 font-[var(--sans)] text-[11px] tracking-[.35em] uppercase text-[var(--moss)]">
          <span class="inline-block w-7 h-px bg-[var(--moss)]"></span>
          <span data-ko-block>지식의 세계수</span>
          <span data-en-block>The World Tree of Knowledge</span>
        </span>

        <h1 class="font-[var(--display)] font-normal leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.01em] mt-5 mb-6 text-[var(--ink)] break-words"
            style="font-size:clamp(26px,3.4vw,50px)" data-ko-block>
          흩어진 문서가<br/>
          한 그루의 <em class="italic text-[var(--moss)]">나무</em>로<br/>
          자라납니다.
        </h1>
        <h1 class="font-[var(--display)] font-normal leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.01em] mt-5 mb-6 text-[var(--ink)] break-words"
            style="font-size:clamp(26px,3.4vw,50px)" data-en-block>
          Scattered docs<br/>
          grow into a single<br/>
          living <em class="italic text-[var(--moss)]">tree</em>.
        </h1>

        <p class="font-[var(--serif)] text-[17px] leading-[1.7] text-[var(--ink-2)] max-w-[520px]" data-ko-block>
          <strong>Gopedia</strong>는 조직의 모든 지식을 하나의 세계수로 엮어내는 RAG 플랫폼입니다.
          뿌리에서 줄기로, 줄기에서 가지로 — 문서·코드·대화가 의미의 결을 따라 연결되고,
          필요한 순간 잎과 열매처럼 답변이 맺힙니다.
        </p>
        <p class="font-[var(--serif)] text-[17px] leading-[1.7] text-[var(--ink-2)] max-w-[520px]" data-en-block>
          <strong>Gopedia</strong> weaves your organization's knowledge into a single World Tree.
          From root to stem to canopy, documents, code, and conversations connect along the grain of meaning —
          and answers ripen like leaves and fruit, exactly when you reach for them.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-7 md:mt-9">
          <a href="#scenarios"
             class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 font-[var(--sans)] text-[13px] font-medium tracking-[.06em] px-5 py-3.5 no-underline rounded-sm transition-colors duration-200 bg-[var(--moss)] text-[var(--paper)] border border-[var(--moss)] hover:bg-[var(--moss-2)] hover:border-[var(--moss-2)]">
            <span data-ko-block>시나리오 보기</span>
            <span data-en-block>See it in action</span>
            <span class="inline-block transition-transform duration-200 group-hover:translate-x-1">&rarr;</span>
          </a>
          <a href="#values"
             class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 font-[var(--sans)] text-[13px] font-medium tracking-[.06em] px-5 py-3.5 no-underline rounded-sm transition-colors duration-200 bg-transparent text-[var(--ink)] border border-[var(--ink-2)] hover:border-[var(--ink)]">
            <span data-ko-block>설계 철학</span>
            <span data-en-block>Design philosophy</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Tree column -->
      <div class="relative w-full max-w-[480px] mx-auto lg:max-w-none lg:ml-auto">
        <GopediaWorldTree locale="ko" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
